App Privacy Policy Tap Guns

This privacy policy concerns the app Tap GunsÂ created by
Happymagenta. We are concerned about safeguarding the
confidentiality of your information. Please read our policy below and let
us know if you have any questions or feedback.

Personal Information
We do not collect any personal information about the users of Tap Guns.
We do not knowingly contact or collect personal information from
children under 13. If you believe we have inadvertently collected such
information, please contact us so we could promptly remove it.

Geo-Location
Tap Guns does not request, collect, or access your location
information.

Links Within Apps
Tap Guns has external links to our games on our website to allow
you to find out more about our products.

In-App Purchases
Tap Guns has in-app purchases, which are absolutely optional and are
standardly protected from accidental purchasing. To increase the protection level and prevent all
in-app purchases on your device go to the User controls section in the
Google Play Store Settings.

Advertising
Tap Guns contains third party advertising as well as advertising of our
own apps. The banners, however, link exclusively to the Google Play.

Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason.
We will notify you of any changes to our Privacy Policy by posting the
new Privacy Policy at our website. You are advised to consult this
Privacy Policy regularly for any changes.

Privacy Questions
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using Tap Guns, or
have questions about our practices, please contact us via email at
al@happymagenta.com.